  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      PTSD (posttraumatic stress disorder) and associated mental health conditions affect both
      veterans and their family members. This study investigates whether group therapy using EFT
      (Emotional Freedom Techniques) and CBT (Cognitive Behavior Therapy) produce reductions in
      PTSD and comorbid symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
